  "summary": "竞技场：决斗回归并加入传奇技能，穿上全新海滩造型，同时解锁全新通用近战武器“天穹穿刺者”。",
  "cover_image": "https://drop-assets.ea.com/images/0164G5DoZzVH3AIbE4cy3A/2ab9f4b2ea5c6bf229e456a29b4f8e98/Copy_of_ApexS25_HauteShot_3840x2160.jpg?im=AspectCrop=(16,9),xPosition=0.25703125,yPosition=0.4847222222222222",
