          "url": "https://drop-assets.ea.com/images/5HmmKqNb782MlRw4nfaTEF/80deeb3af76cf6db0680973d56ae8291/Screenshot_2025-07-08_112611.png?im=AspectCrop=%2816,9%29,xPosition=0.54296875,yPosition=0.42160737812911725",
          "alt": "“天穹穿刺者”通用近战武器展示图。",
          "source": "official"
